content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Oh, it's you.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Hey.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: How's it going, or whatever.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: I don't know.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Insert small talk here.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Nah, mate, I'm messing with you.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Or maybe I'm not.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Who's to say?

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: I mean, me. I'm to say. But I don't really want to.

content.name: {player}
content.dialogue: ...Okay?

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: This feelings shit gets boring, you feel me?

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Like, sure, it's important.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: But sometimes it just makes me want to fucking kick rocks.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: You know?

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Like I know my own deal.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: I don't gotta interrogate my shit.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: I'm already there. I understand it.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: And sure, getting to know someone takes time.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: You gotta talk. You have to get deep, or whatever.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: But it gets so repetitive, right?

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Like we gotta fucking linger over our fears and insecurities.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Hammer in those vulnerabilities.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: And that just sucks.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Because, right, if you know what's wrong with you.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: If you can fucking see it already.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Then do something about it, you know?

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Push yourself. Work at it.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: And don't the people around you wallow in their shit.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: That's nothing. That's pointless.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: If you're good with where you are, great.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Good for you.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: I mean, I think you're lying to yourself.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: But do what you gotta do, you feel?

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: And what I gotta do is stand next to someone in front of a fucking mirror.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: And just look.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: At yourself. At each other.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: And then get real honest about what you're seeing.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Because that's how you move forward, you know.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: It's the only damn way to do it.

options.text: I feel you. We gotta push each other.
I think you need to find someone who wants the version of you that's already here.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: No doubt.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: That's the whole point of being around someone, you know?

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: All of us have something in flux.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: That's human nature, or whatever.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: And you gotta find the person

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Who helps you make the most of that.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Or else you'll just get stuck.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Which sucks.

content.name: {player}
content.dialogue: Yeah.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: And that's not what we're here for, you know?

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: We're here to get different.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Not better. Not worse. Just different.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: And maybe you end up liking that different.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Maybe you fucking hate it.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: But you can always keep getting different.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: As long as you're getting more like yourself.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: You get me?

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Be who you fucking are. Allow yourself to change.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Fuck anyone who says otherwise.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Right?

content.name: {player}
content.dialogue: Right.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Hell yeah.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: You sound like DD.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Which, you know, power to you or whatever.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: But I think you're wrong.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: You're a human being, you know?

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: You're never gonna be one thing forever.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: That would be fucking boring.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Because you gotta be yourself, right.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: But yourself is clay, it's moldable and shit.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Stagnating is boring. It's pointless.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: It doesn't get you anywhere.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: And you can lie to yourself if you want

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: But we're all trying to get somewhere.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: You clearly are, or you wouldn't fucking be here.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Tch. Whatever.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: Good luck with your thing, I guess.

content.name: Gouda
content.dialogue: I don't get it, but maybe I'm not supposed to.
